Citation.sTitle: Isobaric Vapor Liquid Equilibrium Data of Acrylonitrile (1) + Heptan-1-ol (2), Acrylonitrile (1) + Ethanol (2), and Nitrobenzene (1) + Heptan-1-ol (2) at 96.5 kPa
Citation.sAbstract: Isobaric phase equilibrium studies on the binary systems comprising acrylonitrile (1) + heptan-1-ol (2), acrylonitrile (1) + ethanol (2), and heptan-1-ol (1) + nitrobenzene at 96.5 kPa are reported. The activity coefficients are modeled using Wilson s method and the UNIFAC group contribution method.
